data.text: @bethkalexander It’s true, the days are getting longer and spring will be here before we know it! I truly don’t mind waiting my turn for the vaccine, just get a little batty with the Groundhog Day nature of the days sometimes 😝
@christie_gray_ Yes, but: the days are getting longer; we're only 3 months away from spring; and we might get to do normal-ish stuff by summer. Hang in there, Christie! ♥️
